dooyit.parser

Class AddCategoryParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • dooyit.parser.AddCategoryParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserCommons

    public class AddCategoryParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParserCommons
    The AddCategoryParser class takes in an "addcat" command input and returns a Command object. It is needed for adding a category and specifying the category colour. It implements the ParserCommons interface to use the shared constants and share methods.
    Author:
    Annabel
